Coinfinance,provides,users,with,a,Price,Ticker,widget,that,allows,them,to,embed,price,information,for,a,given,cryptocurrency,on,their,websites,or,blogs,Users,can,set,prices,to,appear,in,Bitcoins,U,S,Dollars,Euros,or,Chinese,Yuan,The,widget,can,display,current,price,information,daily,highs,and,lows,and,price,movements,over,the,last,hours